article.headline: Murray State 53, Eastern Illinois 50
article.story: MURRAY, Ky. (AP) -- Ron Kennedy and Bruce Carter each scored nine points to help Murray State beat Eastern Illinois 53-50 on Saturday night in the first conference game of the college basketball season. Shwan Witherspoon added seven points and 11 rebounds for the Racers (2-4, 1-0 Ohio Valley). Romain Martin led Eastern Illinois (2-5, 0-1) with 21 points.
